 of $100-300$\\hmpc, where few other\nconstraints exist.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 16 Jun 1997 16:48:33 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 16 Dec 1997 20:40:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-10-30"}
